bug.short_desc: Sometimes numbers of lines are not aligned properly before and after a diff

long_desc.thetext:
Steps to reproduce: 1. Index attached mercurial repo with sample script 2. Diff versions
Expected result: Regular line numbering. No formating glitches.
Actual result: See attached screen shot. The numbers of lines are not aligned properly before and after a diff.
Used software: OpenGrok 0.10-rc, Apache Tomcat 6.0.29, Sun Java 6 1.6.0_20-b02, Debian GNU/Linux 5.0, Mac OS X 10.6.5, Chrome 7
Created attachment 4422 mercurial clone with sample script
